data.description: Discover this countryside gem offering three bedrooms, two baths and an office/den- flex space nestled on 1.72 acres.  This spectacular home boasts vaulted ceilings throughout the main living area, a formal dining space and a cozy wood burning fireplace in the living room. Wood flooring in the master bedroom with tray ceiling and an ensuite with double vanities, a walk-in shower, and a jetted tub are only a few of the outstanding features of this well-maintained ranch style treasure.  A covered 30' x 46' Pole barn featuring an asphalt driveway, concrete pad with water and electricity and a 30amp hookup is ready to park your RV/Boat or create your dream workshop! This versatile space also includes an enclosed storage area, ideal for all your recreational equipment. The property includes a sprinkler system, new fencing throughout the entire perimeter and has dual gates, with one being fully automated. Beautifully wooded, providing great privacy and situated near SR 200 and 484, this property combines tranquility with convenience. Don't miss this opportunity - schedule a viewing today!
